Interface TopicProducer<K,M>

  • All Superinterfaces:
    AutoCloseable, Closeable
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    TopicProducerImpl, TopicProducerImpl

    public interface TopicProducer<K,M>
extends Closeable
    Wraps access to a message topic Producer, including logic to instantiate the object. This is a wrapper that can be serialized and re-create the Producer remotely.
